Trained Model Artifacts
------------------------
Model adapters or weights produced by fine-tuning on the above data sources
inherit all applicable restrictions from those sources. In particular:

- Artifacts trained on Reddit data are NON-COMMERCIAL only.
- Artifacts trained on Pew NPORS data require Pew attribution.
- Artifacts may not be distributed without confirming compliance with each
  source's terms above.
